name: Galactic Coordinates RA 111m | Dec +6° 6′ 6″
description:
Galactic Coordinates #6 
The Empty Chair

Life goes on by the ruined throne, in a temple built over others, a derelict monument reminiscing about the cycle of civilizations. In the end it is nothing but a magical coordinate in the cosmic magnetic grid. 

4444x4444px PNG

Ink and color markers on paper, 2022.
